commit.message:
configure.in (fastjar_warn_cflags): Set when using gcc.

	* configure.in (fastjar_warn_cflags): Set when using gcc.

	* Makefile.am (AM_CFLAGS): Set to @fastjar_warn_cflags@.

From-SVN: r38255

files.patch:
@@ -1,3 +1,9 @@
+2000-12-14  Kaveh R. Ghazi  <ghazi@caip.rutgers.edu>
+
+	* configure.in (fastjar_warn_cflags): Set when using gcc.
+
+	* Makefile.am (AM_CFLAGS): Set to @fastjar_warn_cflags@.
+
 2000-12-14  Kaveh R. Ghazi  <ghazi@caip.rutgers.edu>
 
 	* compress.c: Include stdlib.h and compress.h.
